headline: Q4 Earnings Recap: Supernus Pharmaceuticals (NASDAQ:SUPN) Tops Branded Pharmaceuticals Stocks
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q4. Today, we are looking at branded pharmaceuticals stocks, starting with Supernus Pharmaceuticals (NASDAQ:SUPN).
